OL,4,Ccrown wobbling during his coronation
OL,6,FThe King joked about "feeling slightly
OL,7,Fanxious" about the weight of the crown
OL,8,Fand it wobbling, as he spoke to women
OL,9,Fwho attended his mother's coronation
OL,10,Fin a new documentary.
OL,12,FThe film follows the story of 50 women
OL,13,Ffrom across Canada who were sponsored
OL,14,Fby Canadian businessman Garfield
OL,15,FWeston to attend the coronation of
OL,16,FQueen Elizabeth II in the summer of
OL,17,F1953.
