OL,6,FThe group, who were around 17 years in
OL,7,Fage, sailed across the Atlantic on the
OL,8,FEmpress of France to reach Liverpool
OL,9,Fwhere they boarded a train down to
OL,10,FLondon for the historic event.
OL,12,FCoronation Girls tracks 12 of the
OL,13,Fwomen, whose average age is 89, as
OL,14,Fthey retraced their steps and returned
OL,15,Fto London in December 2023, where they
OL,16,Fwere surprised by Charles during a
OL,17,Fvisit to Buckingham Palace.
