OL,3,CKing felt 'slightly anxious' about
OL,4,Ccrown wobbling during his coronation
OL,6,FIn the 90-minute documentary, the King
OL,7,Ftold the women he could remember
OL,8,F"quite a lot" of his mother's
OL,9,Fcoronation, despite being just four
OL,10,Fyears old at the time.
OL,12,FHe said: "My grandmother explained
OL,13,Fthings to me while I was there.
OL,15,F"I can remember quite a lot, yes,
OL,16,Fwell, particularly what I was dressed
OL,17,Fin and what the barber did to me
OL,18,Fbefore."
