OL,3,CKing felt 'slightly anxious' about
OL,4,Ccrown wobbling during his coronation
OL,6,FAt one point, Charles joked about the
OL,7,Fpracticalities of wearing the crown,
OL,8,Ftelling the women: "I remember it all
OL,9,Fso well then, because I remember my
OL,10,Fsister and I had bath time in the
OL,11,Fevening.
OL,13,F"My mama used to come up at bath time
OL,14,Fwearing the crown to practice.
OL,16,F"You have to get used to how heavy it
OL,17,Fis.
OL,19,F"I've never forgotten, I can still
OL,20,Fremember it vividly."
