OL,3,CKing felt 'slightly anxious' about
OL,4,Ccrown wobbling during his coronation
OL,6,FHe added: "It is very important to
OL,7,Fwear it for a certain amount of time,
OL,8,Fbecause you get used to it then.
OL,10,F"But the big one that you're crowned
OL,11,Fwith, the St Edward's Crown, it weighs
OL,12,Ffive pounds.
OL,14,F"It is much heavier and taller, so
OL,15,Fthere's always that feeling of feeling
OL,16,Fslightly anxious, in case it wobbles.
OL,18,F"You have to carry it, you have to
OL,19,Flook straight ahead."
