OL,3,CKing felt 'slightly anxious' about
OL,4,Ccrown wobbling during his coronation
OL,6,FThe King was crowned in the 17th
OL,7,Fcentury golden St Edward's Crown by
OL,8,Fthe Archbishop of Canterbury at his
OL,9,Fcoronation in Westminster Abbey in May
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FThe women told the documentary that
OL,13,Ftheir trip to Elizabeth's coronation
OL,14,Fwas "life-changing", "magic" and
OL,15,Fdescribed the moment the new Queen
OL,16,Fpassed them in the gold state coach
OL,17,Fduring procession.
OL,19,F"The crowds were so joyous and so loud
OL,20,Fthey drowned out the marching bands,"
OL,21,Fone said.
