OL,3,CKing felt 'slightly anxious' about
OL,4,Ccrown wobbling during his coronation
OL,6,FAt the time, the late Queen was around
OL,7,Fnine years older than the girls,
OL,8,Fwhich, some said, helped them feel a
OL,9,Fspecial connection with the new
OL,10,Fmonarch.
OL,12,FIn June 2022, the group wrote a letter
OL,13,Fto Elizabeth where they asked if they
OL,14,Fcould have tea with her a few months
OL,15,Fbefore she died.
OL,17,FThe documentary, which explores themes
OL,18,Fof enduring friendship and the impact
OL,19,Fthe historic event had on the young
OL,20,Fwomen, will be aired on Boxing Day on
OL,21,FWNED PBS in Canada.
